{"id":3587,"date":"2025-12-12T04:22:05","date_gmt":"2025-12-12T04:22:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/attendo.in\/?post_type=addon&#038;p=3587"},"modified":"2026-03-31T10:41:19","modified_gmt":"2026-03-31T10:41:19","slug":"payroll","status":"publish","type":"addon","link":"https:\/\/attendo.in\/addon\/payroll\/","title":{"rendered":"Advanced Payroll: Automated Deductions, Tax Slabs, and Attendance Sync"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"3587\" class=\"elementor elementor-3587\" data-elementor-post-type=\"addon\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0367fcc e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0367fcc\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5812c73 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5812c73\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What is the Advanced Payroll Addon?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a09386a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a09386a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The Advanced Payroll Addon is <strong>a functional expansion module for the ecosystem that automates complex financial calculations.<\/strong> It transforms manual data entry into an automated workflow by integrating Biometric Attendance, Tax Compliance, and Payroll Advance logic. This module eliminates 100% of manual calculation risks in monthly salary generation.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c2d4478 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c2d4478\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-296edb8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"296edb8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How does a Payroll Advance function in Attendo?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5d1be9e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5d1be9e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A Payroll Advance functions by allowing employees to access earned wages before the scheduled payday through a five-step automated cycle.<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Request:<\/b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Employees submit requests via the<\/span> <b>PWA Mobile Interface<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Approval:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 Administrators review the request against the<\/span> <b>Company Advance Policy<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Disbursement:\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The system processes the funds instantly to the employee.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Auto-Deduction:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 The payroll engine subtracts the advance from the next net salary.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><b>Audit Trail:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 The digital ledger records the transaction for transparency.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c3d45d6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c3d45d6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c5a08d8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c5a08d8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How does the system automate salary deductions?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3871b29 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3871b29\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Attendo automates salary deductions by applying\u00a0 <\/span><b>Pre-Tax <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and\u00a0 <\/span><b>Post-Tax<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> rules to the gross earnings. According to\u00a0 <\/span><b>PwC\u2019s 2024 Global Payroll Survey<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, automation reduces payroll error rates by\u00a0 <\/span><b>35%<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 compared to manual systems.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Configure Rules:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 Set fixed amounts, variable limits, or percentages.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Assign Schedules:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 Map deductions to monthly, weekly, or daily cycles.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Identify Mismatches:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 The system flags discrepancies between basic pay and total salary.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><b>Force Generate:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 The software auto-fills unpaid days during bulk salary creation.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-843c585 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"843c585\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8cc588d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8cc588d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Does Attendo calculate overtime automatically?\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1405bc1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1405bc1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Yes, Attendo calculates overtime automatically by syncing real-time attendance logs with standard shift parameters<\/strong>. The system identifies hours worked beyond the shift limit and applies fixed or percentage-based rates to the basic salary.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Hours Tracking:\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Overtime is derived from\u00a0 <\/span><b>ZKTeco\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> or\u00a0 <\/span><b>Anviz\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> device logs.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Rate Application:\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Administrators set overtime types for daily or weekly periods.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><b>Salary Integration:\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Overtime pay appears as a distinct line item on the\u00a0 <\/span><b>Pay Slip<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d38bb61 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"d38bb61\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-919dc04 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"919dc04\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How do tax slabs and compliance rules work?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d461de2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d461de2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tax slabs work by categorizing employee income into defined ranges with specific percentage rates.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Income Ranges:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 Define taxable boundaries and validity dates.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Rebate Slabs:\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Configure tax reductions based on\u00a0 <\/span><b>Age\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and\u00a0 <\/span><b>Gender\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> criteria.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Net Calculation:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 The system determines tax after subtracting\u00a0 <\/span><b>Pre-Tax\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> deductions.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><b>Document Generation:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 Every cycle produces a compliant\u00a0 <\/span><b>Tax Slip\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for the employee.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c6d521a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c6d521a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5d45b1d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5d45b1d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Comparison: Basic Payroll vs. Advanced Payroll Addon<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d6c67fb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d6c67fb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><b>Feature<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><b>Basic Payroll<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><b>Advanced Payroll Addon<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><b>Attendance Sync<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manual Entry<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><b>100% Automated<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><b>Tax Compliance<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Not Included<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><b>Custom Tax Slabs &amp; Rebates<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><b>Deduction Types<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fixed Only<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><b>Pre-Tax &amp; Post-Tax Rules<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><b>Payslip Documents<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Single Format<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><b>Dual Slips (Pay &amp; Tax)<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><b>Overtime Logic<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manual<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><b>Automatic Hour Calculation<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b0aa9c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"1b0aa9c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-463edc1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"463edc1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why upgrade to the Advanced Payroll Addon today?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c061707 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c061707\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Upgrading to <\/span><b>Advanced Payroll<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> provides total control over growing teams by removing the &#8220;Time-Per-Employee&#8221; burden from HR.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Save Time:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 Automate\u00a0 <\/span><b>Pay Slip <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and\u00a0 <\/span><b>Tax Slip <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">generation instantly.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Ensure Accuracy:\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Utilize\u00a0 <\/span><b>Mismatch Flags<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to spot gross salary errors.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Improve Morale:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 Offer\u00a0 <\/span><b>Payroll Advances\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> with 0% repayment friction.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Maintain Compliance:\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Update tax rules to match local legal requirements.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"template":"","class_list":["post-3587","addon","type-addon","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"\/data\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/addon\/3587","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"\/data\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/addon"}],"about":[{"href":"\/data\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/addon"}],"version-history":[{"count":53,"href":"\/data\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/addon\/3587\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4119,"href":"\/data\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/addon\/3587\/revisions\/4119"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"\/data\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3587"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}